snippet.textDisplay: Masuma Anwar, is a doctor by profession and specializing in pediatrics, belongs from Kashmir. Masuma has come a long way in the world of Pakistani music industry. She is great at sufi, folk and ghazal genre which actually raise high bars for her. She sang many famous folk songs like ‘Ve Asaan Tenu Ki Akhna’, ‘Ve main chori chori’ and ‘’Neyu La leya’ of the legendary singers which are truly loved by people. Her voice appeals and touches the soul and does affect the hearts.

snippet.textDisplay:
I never liked Masuma, her voice just doesn't get me, but she is amazing. Javed Bashir could have done a lot more alone if this was his solo. Shehzad  voice and talent has been used by many commercials and video but his narration failed to make a mark.  
Music was running so fast, all three were running with it.  It was blessing in disguise of editing department, though wasn't bad at all.

Composition: 7/10, Singing 7/10 Overall, 7/10.
